-- Disney's Eisner in E-Mail Said `Millionaire' as Important as Pro Football
-- Edvard Pettersson
-- 2010-06-16T19:02:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/disney-s-eisner-in-e-mail-said-millionaire-as-important-as-pro-football.html

          
          
             Walt Disney Co.’s former Chief
Executive Officer Michael Eisner said “Who Wants to Be a
Millionaire?” was as important as the National Football League
to ABC and would turn around the television network, according
to e-mails introduced in the trial over profits from the game
show.  
